   <conbody>
      <conbodydiv class="- topic/bodydiv concept/conbodydiv ">
         <section class="- topic/section ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">Black start is an optional feature. With black start it
is possible to start the system with only the batteries when the rectifier
mains <ph platform="PxW" class="- topic/ph ">and bypass mains are </ph>
               <ph platform="SDC" class="- topic/ph ">is </ph>unavailable.</p>
            <p platform="PxW" class="- topic/p ">There are two different
types of black starts:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Black start installed on the inverter input switch</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Black start installed on the battery breaker</p>
                  </li>
               </ul>
               <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">Check the status of the respective switch depending on the type.</note>
            </p>
         </section>
         <section class="- topic/section ">
            <title class="- topic/title ">Check Before Performing a Black Start</title>
            <p class="- topic/p ">Check that the system is in the following status before proceeding:</p>
            <table pgwide="1" class="- topic/table ">
               <tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                  <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="50.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
